  92:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c **** 
  93:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c ****     Releases ownership of the mutual exclusion lock, and
  94:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c ****     restores the previous task priority level.
  95:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c ****     
  96:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c **** Arguments:
  97:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c **** 
