  99:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c ****     
 100:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c **** Returns:
 101:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c **** 
 102:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c ****     Lock unowned
 103:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c **** 
 104:../Backend/gnu-efi-3.0.9/lib/lock.c **** --*/
